column5: hahaha - I saw this this one.  Gosh, Hes got to be 2 stories above the water. How the heck is he going to get a fish up that far?
Pretty big guy to be pranking, too... When my buddy and I are trolling, I like to lean back, stretch, and grab his line when he's not looking..he most decidedly does NOT like it
Awesome.   I do that to my dad when we are ice fishing.
Last pri ck that did that too me wears a kilt in his spare time,,,,
